      <div class="q-text">In the \(xy\)-plane, the parabola \(y = x^2 - 6x + 14\) intersects the line \(y = 2x + k\) at exactly one point. What is the value of \(k\)?</div>
      <ul class="q-options">
        <li><button onclick="checkAnswer(this,'A','math')">A) \(-2\)</button></li>
        <li><button onclick="checkAnswer(this,'B','math')">B) \(2\)</button></li>
